    • Method Detail

      • castOrCopy

        public static DefaultDimension castOrCopy(Dimension object)
        Returns a SIS metadata implementation with the values of the given arbitrary implementation. This method performs the first applicable action in the following choices:
        • If the given object is null, then this method returns null.
        • Otherwise if the given object is already an instance of DefaultDimension, then it is returned unchanged.
        • Otherwise a new DefaultDimension instance is created using the copy constructor and returned. Note that this is a shallow copy operation, since the other metadata contained in the given object are not recursively copied.
        Parameters:
        object - The object to get as a SIS implementation, or null if none.
        Returns:
        A SIS implementation containing the values of the given object (may be the given object itself), or null if the argument was null.
